The RuneScape Wiki also has an article on: rsw:Herbert Dunwich

Herbert Dunwich is the author of The weeping. He lived sometime during the God Wars. The weeping recounts his experience with a mysterious weeping creature encountered under the northern shore of Forinthry.

Trivia[edit | edit source]

  • In RuneScape Herbert Dunwich is the name of the author of the Pestilent journal.
